# virtualenvwrapper

> A tool to work with virtual environments.

## Work on a virtual environment.
```bash
workon <name>
```

## Stop working on a virtual environment.
```bash
deactivate
```

## List all virtual environments.
```bash
# -l long mode
# -b brief mode
lsvirtualenv [-l|-b]
```

## Destroy a virtual environment.
```bash
rmvirtualenv <name>
```

## Copy a virtual environment.
```bash
cpvirtualenv <name>
```
